
This Directory Provides implemenation of a chat-bot utilising open source model phi3 along with langchain.

Please ensure all the requirements mentioned in the requirements.txt have been installed.

You are required to install Ollama first 

and then run the command 
ollama pull phi3
Once it has been downloaded, run 
ollama run phi3

Include your pdf files in a folder and replace the path in db_creator.py for the same 

Execute the command 'python3 db_creator.py' to create the index for pdf files.

Executing main.py instantiates the chat with the LLM.